g.text: This workflow creates a report about a workflow by extrracting all metadata information about that workflow and combining it with an image of the
4 workflows along with the XMLs containing their metadata as well as their workflow images are contained in the workflow_documentation
directory. You can select a workflow's XML and have a report created for that
The example uses the Analyze Workflow Summary component to extract metadata from the XML file.
To create a report on your own workflow, open the workflow then go to FILE > EXPORT > EXPORT WORKFLOW SUMMARY. choose XML and a
location. To create an image of your workflow, go to FILE > EXPORT > EXPORT IMAGE.
You can now point this workflow to the files you have created and generate your own report.
Note that there is a fully automated example for both generating and extracting multiple workflows using KNIME Server available on
